data.description: Experience the best of Arizona living in this 4bed, 3 bath oasis located in the desirable Rincon Trails community. This property offers the ideal combination of space and privacy, with a large extended length 2 car garage and an expansive 2-story layout. Cook and entertain in style in the spacious kitchen, where open-concept living takes center stage. Discover the ultimate retreat with a beautiful pool and no neighbors behind, providing unmatched relaxation. Located in the Award-Winning Vail School District.
